        "subject": "LU-1060 mdt: fail VBR during recovery if miss target",
        "message": "LU-1060 mdt: fail VBR during recovery if miss target\n\nDuring VBR phase, if some target missed, it quite possbile caused\nby some unrecovered RPC (related client unconnected or failed to\nrecovery such RPC). Such case should be regarded as target version\nunmatched, and the client should be evicted.\n\nSigned-off-by: Fan Yong <yong.fan@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I9e126de1a20e446bcdc2faf425d323843277ce4f\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
